title: #337 - Javier Vazquez
description:
Javier Vazquez, former UFC fighter and owner of Gracie Jiu-Jitsu Rancho - Cucamonga,who is competing at the EBI 5 Sunday December 13, 2015 at the Orpheum Theater in Los Angeles, joins Joey Diaz and Lee Syatt live in studio.
